						p
							| Subscribe to our feeds:
						p
							a(href='/blog/rss.xml')
								img(src='https://www.sharelatex.com/blog/images/icons/feed.png')
								| RSS
							| or
							a(href='/blog/atom.xml')
								img(src='https://www.sharelatex.com/blog/images/icons/feed.png')
								| Atom
						p
